es, solve puzzles and try to advance to the next objectives. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival elements with full inventory system, objectives, clue-findings and tools to help you in escaping. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzles to unsolve, mysteries to uncover. Use your mind to overcome obstacles that you will find in your way. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stealth System: Try and sneak through the terrifying enemies that can only be seen by scanning them. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hiding System: Hide from the enemies under tables, while trying to stay quiet as they can hear you from your microphone when you are in hiding mode. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gut Wrecking Moments: Walking on broken glass can make noises that the enemy may hear, same as moving crates or knocking over objects. all these things can give away your position. Try to evade them or use them as your advantages. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory Management: Find supplies, upgrades, health packs and more items will be vital for your survival.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your microphone to call for 'Roy'. If your dog is near, he will bark back to you.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/50022fa83b30b9e2a11531443c59dab8.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/50022fa83b30b9e2a11531443c59dab8.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/50022fa83b30b9e2a11531443c59dab8.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Search the sewers and tunnels for your lost dog, as any loving owner should do.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/cb6a54d928bca1dd80770e9f098b3046.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/cb6a54d928bca1dd80770e9f098b3046.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/cb6a54d928bca1dd80770e9f098b3046.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find guns, ammo and weapons to protect yourself against the bigger threats.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/99758aeb6d5b3564c53093f694f4f7ef.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/99758aeb6d5b3564c53093f694f4f7ef.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/99758aeb6d5b3564c53093f694f4f7ef.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage your inventory, find supplies and combine them to help you in the journey.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/165b269b97ba99492786fd62ae4453e6.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/165b269b97ba99492786fd62ae4453e6.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/165b269b97ba99492786fd62ae4453e6.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gut-wrecking moments with an enemy that can hear you and your voice.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/ade29bd6e8b657e1be355278604a6fa3.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/ade29bd6e8b657e1be355278604a6fa3.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/ade29bd6e8b657e1be355278604a6fa3.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Protect yourself not only from enemies, but also from infected rats that will hurt you.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/e839c2b329683317546e41aaee028c18.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/e839c2b329683317546e41aaee028c18.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/e839c2b329683317546e41aaee028c18.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hide in lockers, under tables and in furniture to stay hidden from the enemy. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/1029d342966c1f1dfe4a742f2fff9e8b.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/1029d342966c1f1dfe4a742f2fff9e8b.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/1029d342966c1f1dfe4a742f2fff9e8b.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Creepy environment with narrow and claustrophobic corridors and rooms. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/6ce7192a0c36a6a2f156f982494ecd9f.poster.avif?t=1753743712\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/6ce7192a0c36a6a2f156f982494ecd9f.webm?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657600/extras/6ce7192a0c36a6a2f156f982494ecd9f.mp4?t=1753743712\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotten Flesh is a horror survival game made by one developer at Steelkrill Studio. This is objective-finding game with puzzles to solve, and terrifying encounters, inventory system, stamina, pistols, shooting mechanics, microphone input and a lot more features. If you can, please submit your feedback and report any bugs and this will really help speed up the progress of the development! Thank you so much.</p>",
